title: Being Lucky vs Being Intentional
itunes:title: Being Lucky vs Being Intentional
description:
Episode 289 -  Luck is a BS word. Luck is found in gambling and the lottery but not in success. Intention is found in success. Listen to this episode to understand how to be more intentional and plan out your road to success.
